<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmaccaturtthānvayarājasiṁhassamma <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> bavirōdhisaṁhaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> goṁkkakṣamādhī <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> janmā 
<lb n="2"/>sauṁdaryyarēkhāvijitāṁggajanmā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> yasya śrīgiri<unclear>jē</unclear>śvarasya vipulā śrīpādapadmadvayē bhaktiryyō velanā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁṭicōḍanṛpatērānaṁdadō naṁdanaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> guṁḍāṁbāmaṇibhūsamudgatalasadvaiḍūryyabhāsvanmaṇiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ḥ khaṇḍitavairirapratihatō bhūpālavidyādharaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasya nṛpamaṇḍanasya pradhānapatnī mahāsatī mu
<lb n="5" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> guṇamaṇikhaṇira <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> dēvī <unclear>nāgāṁ</unclear>bikā śubhā<unclear>cā</unclear>ravatī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē nidhitarkkadikparimi
<lb n="6" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear>cā</unclear>ṣāḍhaśuddhāṣṭamīsukravārā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>vanārāyaṇaprītyai <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> māḥ pradīpaminabhūcaṁdradyutārasthiraṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrīmattribhuvanacakrava
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rtti śrīkulōttuṁgacōḍadēvara vijayarājya samaṁtsaraṁbulu 15 śrāhi <unclear>paṁḍa</unclear>rāju dēvulu nāgaladēvi Akhaṁḍadīpamunaku
<lb n="9"/>peṭṭina birudumāḍalu 12 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēkoni yī dēvara paricārakulu sūreyu bhāvanārāyaṇuṁḍunuṁ bermmāḍiyu dāmō
<lb n="10" break="no"/>daruṁḍu nallabavvanayu gōviṁddiyu rāghapakāmanayu guṁḍanārāyaṇuṁḍunu<note n="70-1">The syllables pottavaḍa are written below the line.</note>pottavaḍa mrāneyuṁdama putrānupautrikamu
<lb n="11" break="no"/>gā nitya māneṁḍu neyi vōyaṁggalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
